---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — HomeRecordingGear"
  description="Who runs HomeRecordingGear and why you should trust these recommendations."
>
  <article class="space-y-6 text-gray-700">
    <header class="space-y-3">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">About this site</h1>
    </header>

    <p>
      HomeRecordingGear exists because the gear advice online is mostly terrible —
      either affiliate-stuffed listicles recommending 30 products without opinions,
      or gear-nerd deep dives that assume you already know what a preamp is.
    </p>

    <p>
      This site is for people who are setting up their first home studio and need
      someone to just tell them what to buy. I research the gear, pick the best options,
      and write honest recommendations without the filler.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">How recommendations are made</h2>
    <p>
      Every product I recommend has to pass three tests: it has to actually sound good (not just
      "good for the price"), it has to have consistent build quality across units, and I have to
      be comfortable recommending it to someone spending real money for the first time.
      I don't recommend gear just because it pays a higher commission.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">Affiliate disclosure</h2>
    <p>
      This site earns a commission when you click a link and buy something — typically 3–10%
      depending on the retailer. This doesn't affect the price you pay. It's how the site
      stays free and ad-free.
    </p>
    <p>
      I only link to products I'd actually recommend. If a product pays a better commission
      but isn't the best option, I recommend the better option.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>
